        <title>Standard Torque Charts</title>
        <specpara>
            <caution>
                <para>To prevent engine damage, do not use this standard torque chart with other International brand
                    engines or engines made by other manufacturers.
                </para>
            </caution>
        </specpara>
        <para>Standard torque chart provides tightening values for all hardware that do not require special torque.
        </para>
